Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:55.84,PW2,,0,0,0,,{\fs25.5\fax-0.1\frz340.3\move(1221,516.2,1221,391.5,8,3656)}·預先偵查並設置陷阱，更快掌握敵人\N的配置，保持對己方有利的戰況。\N　　　　（友情值越高必殺技和陷阱的效果就會越強）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:55.84,PW2,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\fax-0.1\frz337\move(779.9,345.1,781.5,222,8,3656)}　通過獲得市民們的協助，以及通過開發強力的道具，就能夠預先洞察到敵人\N的陷阱並破壞。英雄們所居住的美好的城市，是需要住民們的協助的！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:55.84,PW2,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\fax-0.1\frz333.6\move(616.5,636,616.5,514.5,28,3656)}在城市裡發生的戰鬥會存在把市民也捲入其中的危險性！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:55.84,PW2,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\fax-0.1\frz334.1\move(433.5,877.5,433.5,756,28,3656)}　　紅…擅長直接攻擊，\N　　攻守均衡以及能進行\N　　只有主角才可以的輔\N　　助，可以裝備主角限\N　　定的傳說中的道具，\N　擁有自動回復能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:55.84,PW2,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\fax-0.1\frz341.7\move(1187.9,844.4,1189.5,724.5,8,3656)}藍…擅長間接攻擊的攻擊特化型。雖然移動速度很快，但是防禦和紙糊\N的一樣弱。自己被逼入絕境時所能發動的逆轉型必殺技是其魅力所在。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:55.84,PW2,,0,0,0,,{\fs19.5\fax-0.1\frz340\move(1026,1119,1026,997.5,28,3656)}　黑…物理特化型並\N　且攻守數值都很高，\N不過移動很慢。因\N為其本人很不靈光\N所以有無法使用的\N道具。擁有能夠改\N　　變地形效果的特殊能力。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:55.84,PW2,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\fax-0.1\frz333.3\move(375,1153.5,375,1032,28,3656)}　　　　　　　綠…在探索方面很出類拔萃。\N　　　　　　　因為其聰明頭腦好用所以道具\N　　　　　　　的使用效果也會提升，也很擅\N　　　　　　　長設置·解除陷阱。不過攻守\N數值都很低。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:55.84,PW2,,0,0,0,,{\fs21\fax-0.1\frz340\move(985.5,1144.5,985.5,1023,28,3656)}粉…間接攻擊類，輔助特化型
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.70,0:04:57.70,PW3,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.1\frz353.8\move(936,525,913.5,525,26,1986)}明天去賞櫻花
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.46,0:00:04.00,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.30,0:00:09.09,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}已經在「EAGLE JUMP」工作了整整一年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.02,0:00:11.93,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\pos(960,1080)}我也已經習慣了在公司的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:19.64,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\pos(960,1089)}我是妳的前輩涼風青葉  請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.27,0:00:22.90,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是妳的前輩涼風青葉  請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.40,0:00:24.00,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:27.56,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我為人前輩的一天終於到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.28,0:00:29.06,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:29.98,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.98,0:00:32.91,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}遠山姊  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.96,0:00:37.54,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\pos(960,1089)}一想到今天我就是別人的前輩了  有點緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.16,0:00:40.37,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今年沒有新人喔
Comment: 0,0:00:46.87,0:00:48.87,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,+0.16s
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.03,0:00:49.86,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:51.83,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}畢竟我們不是什麼大公司
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:00:55.59,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}做蠢事的樣子被看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:00:58.14,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我不會告訴別人的  不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.63,0:01:00.12,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}對了  要喝點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.88,0:01:01.81,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.11,0:01:04.63,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那就來杯咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.14,0:01:06.69,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}加砂糖和牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.72,0:01:08.44,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:16.97,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}八神姊  在公司過夜了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.69,0:01:22.27,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:26.61,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有份工作我想快些做完
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.35,0:01:31.57,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一年前的這個時候好像也是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:33.49,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一年前？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.70,0:01:37.24,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喔  已經四月了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.61,0:01:42.73,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我已經對只穿內褲的八神姊見怪不怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:44.21,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.49,0:01:46.79,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}請…請快找條裙子穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.93,0:01:49.01,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哎？！突然怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.28,0:01:51.15,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}早安  小光妳要喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:53.47,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要  謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:58.39,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}青葉的那杯是黑咖啡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:00.50,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:03.94,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}黑咖啡不好喝  所以加了砂糖和牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.13,0:02:06.79,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妳也稍微成長了一些嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.37,0:02:11.03,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}早安！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.93,0:02:13.09,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:16.43,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今天是不是會有新人要來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:19.49,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我可要打起精神才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:24.01,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是妳的前輩筱田初  請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:25.07,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.49,0:02:27.87,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}叫我初姊就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:30.03,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.45,0:02:32.79,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}初姊  妳剛才看到我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.05,0:02:34.11,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哎  看到什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:36.69,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.27,0:02:38.63,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}結音  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:41.07,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎麼了  有新人要來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:42.11,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.44,0:02:44.42,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我得做好準備免得緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:46.15,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不  其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.26,0:02:49.01,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}新…人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:52.23,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}日富美前輩  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:54.17,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}會不會是壞孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:02:57.25,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}該…該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.29,0:03:00.95,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是不是  今年沒有新人的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:04.48,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什麼呀  原來是初搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.82,0:03:07.94,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}現在既覺得有些可惜  又鬆了一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:12.32,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣的話  今年小青葉還是最小的後輩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.81,0:03:14.07,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:18.03,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}小光  差不多該把裙子穿上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:20.58,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不得了  忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.83,0:03:24.29,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}八神姊  在公司過夜了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:26.96,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}現在工作沒那麼忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:29.71,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只是在給其他組幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:33.26,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我就是想一鼓作氣地把事做完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:38.30,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在新作開始之前儘量多做掉一些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:41.51,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}新作的企劃還沒有確定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:44.77,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}葉月姊的準備似乎要晚些才能做好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:47.99,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}吶  水雲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.34,0:03:51.82,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妳知不知道妳的主人在考慮什麼樣的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.95,0:03:56.74,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妳們知道葉月姊在哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.14,0:03:59.20,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}海子姊  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:02.23,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}葉月姊應該已經來上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:04.23,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}水雲也在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.56,0:04:06.63,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:10.55,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我還想讓她早點檢查一下新作的測試版呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.05,0:04:13.05,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不用這麼著急嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:15.47,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}反正新作開始之後一定會很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:18.23,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}當然想趁現在多玩一玩的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:20.09,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妳嘴上這麼說著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.39,0:04:22.68,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看樣子是又在公司過夜工作了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.25,0:04:27.60,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}順便說一句  前幾天我進山裡通宵玩生存遊戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.23,0:04:29.69,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真…真有精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:30.86,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}對呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:33.99,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在變忙之前還是痛痛快快玩一場更好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:36.24,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不用說妳一定一直在玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:37.82,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:41.16,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}新作真的很快就要開始製作了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:44.99,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:46.05,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}別動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:54.89,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明天  去賞櫻花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:04:57.91,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:04:59.77,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明明只差一點就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:01.84,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}卻一點幹勁也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:03.93,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}工作一點進展都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:10.95,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}瀧本在笑  好…好可愛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:13.82,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}咳  妳們聊得很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:15.51,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}葉月姊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:17.09,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:18.89,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妳們在聊什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:23.93,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}初姊提議我們試著做一些更方便運動的模型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:27.17,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}日富美前輩出了很多點子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:28.43,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:32.73,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒…沒什麼厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:37.67,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}抱歉  太可愛了忍不住就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:42.43,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不過瀧本的表情變得更溫柔了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:44.22,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我覺得這是好事喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:45.83,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.16,0:05:49.85,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那個…剛才我們也聊到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:53.60,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}新作會是什麼樣子的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:59.83,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雖然拜託海子做了很多測試版本當參考
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:01.57,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但還是很難做決定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:03.03,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:08.66,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妳們能做出好的企劃書的話  也會被採用喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:10.54,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.67,0:06:13.09,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那我要做戰隊題材的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.01,0:06:16.09,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是魔法少女也很難割捨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:17.19,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看妳滿腦都是這些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.59,0:06:18.50,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.97,0:06:21.13,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我更想做嚴肅風格的遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:24.07,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我果然還是想要做幻想類的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:27.43,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什麼都想做的話就會很難抉擇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:28.87,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}瀧本想做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:34.65,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我也…和小青葉…一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:37.13,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:39.67,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}果然還是已經做習慣了的幻想類遊戲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:43.32,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}對了  明天我們要去賞櫻花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:46.73,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}應該也會邀請其它組的人來參加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:48.43,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可以的話葉月姊也一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:51.79,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那可一定要帶我一起去  我會帶慰問品喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:53.62,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.69,0:07:01.03,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嘿嘿嘿  發現目標
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:03.31,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}該怎麼嚇唬她一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:08.47,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}被發現了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:10.93,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不…不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.19,0:07:13.79,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}離得這麼遠應該不會被發現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:15.73,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}巧合  是巧合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:17.85,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}咦  不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:21.02,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:21.83,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}發現妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:24.28,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:26.57,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}竟然把視線從目標身上移開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:29.41,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妳…妳在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:30.77,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在妳後面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:36.17,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Bang！其實是在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:44.29,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妳還是老樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:47.47,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}白玉餡蜜看起來好好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:48.59,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:49.95,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可以吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:52.25,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.19,0:07:56.47,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就當是在給動物餵食就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:02.33,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好吃  好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:04.74,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那  回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:07.53,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:11.05,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哎呀  妳這是害羞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:13.07,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}才沒有害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:17.83,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}知道了  我吃就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:20.92,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那  張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:23.53,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}才怪  不給妳吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:27.43,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}玩笑  我開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:34.93,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那麼  今天找我商量的是什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:39.44,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大學的功課我可幫不上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:41.15,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:45.95,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那個…妳不會笑我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:48.05,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}視情況可能會笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:49.36,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}壞心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.47,0:08:51.37,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:53.49,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}櫻小姐製作的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:54.97,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:56.62,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:09:00.15,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}畫面的確是蠻厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.73,0:09:03.49,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒辦法嘛  我又不會畫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.33,0:09:06.13,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是動作蠻流暢的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:09.79,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快看  可以跳  還可以攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:13.01,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}又停住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.23,0:09:14.06,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:18.68,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在寫程式上遇到了問題才把我叫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:22.02,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}之前就三不五時運行不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.53,0:09:25.69,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但運行的時候一直都能運行的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.99,0:09:28.57,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}來這邊給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.87,0:09:32.82,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那就麻煩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:37.16,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}注意看這裡  能明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:40.71,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}同樣的處理重複了好幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:43.03,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}原來如此  不愧是專業程式設計師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.94,0:09:46.61,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妳覺得寫程式有意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.93,0:09:50.47,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不清楚  太難了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:54.55,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是  我現在有點明白小青的心情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.33,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雖然和畫畫不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:59.31,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但這樣看著遊戲慢慢成型也很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:00.39,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還有就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:04.77,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}程式設計師那種「千萬不要發現BUG」的想法也有些明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:07.11,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}之前什麼都不明白就參與DEBUG了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:12.21,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不過  找不到BUG反而讓人不安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.47,0:10:14.57,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.66,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有BUG出現是正常情況
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:21.04,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一點點修復改進才是理所當然的流程
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:23.79,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒有BUG反倒不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:25.29,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:27.46,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有BUG是正常的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:29.80,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我有點安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:33.77,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而且通過BUG的情況也能看出程式設計師的水準
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.99,0:10:35.51,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我知道自己技術差啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:38.99,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不過  改進之後再拿給我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:44.83,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}難道說我蠻有潛力？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:46.59,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妳也太樂觀了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:49.32,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這件事要對小青保密喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:52.95,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}至少在這個遊戲完成之前要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:10:54.29,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:11:01.12,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雖然以前的表情很僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:05.13,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但我的努力…被大家認可了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:06.71,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}宗次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.62,0:11:16.47,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}瀧本想做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:22.43,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我也…和小青葉…一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.02,0:11:28.21,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可我還是…沒能說出自己的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:33.13,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣的表情可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:42.12,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}關於前作開發的感想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:43.13,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:48.17,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}按慣例要在四月詢問大家對去年工作的感想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.75,0:11:50.63,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好的地方和需要反省的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.15,0:11:52.67,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}或者是今後的目標也可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.18,0:11:54.01,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有什麼想說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:58.60,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那個…如果在這裡說了奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:00.47,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}對我的評價會下降嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.85,0:12:03.01,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒有這種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.81,0:12:04.52,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:08.05,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}為什麼我們的小組裡全是女性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:11.35,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}被妳發現了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:14.28,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但這樣也蠻不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:17.05,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也就是說  是按葉月姊的喜好來選人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:18.40,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:20.91,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有好好地按工作能力和合適程度來挑選喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:22.87,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}全是女性只是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:25.63,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}葉月姊就是愛開玩笑  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:26.73,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:29.88,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果有男人進公司  把八神給搶走了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.11,0:12:32.01,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}遠山能受得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.57,0:12:34.42,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我的事無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:37.59,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}涼風  還有什麼感想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:39.13,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:40.35,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:44.83,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}能在憧憬的八神姊的手下工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:48.75,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}讓我覺得這一年過得很充實
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:51.69,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希望自己能多做些貢獻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:55.99,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也想要多做一些村民以外的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:57.28,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:13:00.62,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不過  再貪心一點也可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:02.08,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}貪心？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:04.16,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是指工資嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:06.46,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那也很重要啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:08.54,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}反省？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.11,0:13:13.35,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我倒是覺得這次進行得蠻順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:17.51,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妳們兩人也很有默契  是個好團隊喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:20.51,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯  是凜一直都在幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:21.61,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:25.13,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣的關係也不一定會永遠持續下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:27.35,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}小光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.65,0:13:31.25,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如…如果妳想要和別人結婚了  要和我說實話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:33.37,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這也是沒辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:36.94,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}果然還是不能招男人進來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:40.53,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}目標…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:42.03,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:46.87,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:53.07,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我想…克服…溝通障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:13:55.29,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯嗯  我支持妳喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:56.79,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}請嚴肅一點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:13:59.65,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:05.45,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我昨天…雖然說自己和小青葉的想法一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.81,0:14:10.51,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但其實…我更喜歡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:15.25,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}現代風的…時尚的世界觀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:17.19,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:20.40,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:23.07,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒事  我只是有點意外
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:25.78,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妳能把這些告訴我很好  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:27.66,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我會好好參考的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:30.27,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:33.79,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妳在面談的時候做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:36.21,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}對了  瀧本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.65,0:14:38.71,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妳有沒有興趣做角色組的組長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:42.87,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}下一作遠山會擔任製作人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:44.80,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}八神來當美術總監
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.43,0:14:49.39,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以我想讓其她人來擔任角色組組長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:52.67,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我們也不會勉強妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:57.73,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}她好像太吃驚了  沒聽進去的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:00.32,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我來當主程式員？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.26,0:15:04.03,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這安排蠻妥當的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:07.17,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妳這份坦坦蕩蕩的自信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:09.55,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要是能分一半給瀧本就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:11.04,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雖然不太懂妳在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:13.46,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但要我當主程式員的話有一個條件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:14.63,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:17.92,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果妳敢亂修改就要接受懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:19.27,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}彈額頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:21.89,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有修改也是無可奈何的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.11,0:15:23.68,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妳希望做出無聊的遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:25.01,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:28.26,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我只是希望妳修改的時更慎重一些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:30.85,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}過去總是突然跑來我們組的隔間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:35.02,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}笑眯眯地說「有新的修改喔」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.44,0:15:36.27,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妳能明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:39.23,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我們又要重頭做起時的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.64,0:15:41.79,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}又要通宵趕工時的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:45.95,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒想到總是一臉嚴肅的妳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.18,0:15:48.74,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還有這種為同伴著想的可愛之處嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:50.13,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}小海子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.67,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妳是覺得這樣懲罰妳更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:54.63,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}彈額頭就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:57.29,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這次會由我也會參與項目管理的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:16:00.00,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不會再發展成讓妳們為難的狀況啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:04.87,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}說來女孩子來彈我的額頭其實是一種獎賞呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:06.76,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算彈我額頭的是海子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.59,0:16:12.61,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}談判成立了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:16.13,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}此時的葉月雫  還未曾知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:22.53,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}自己會後悔接受被彈額頭這件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:25.35,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我寫好企劃書了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:26.53,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}企劃書？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:28.95,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯  昨天我是有說過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:32.49,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不過我倒是沒想到妳只花一晚上就能完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:40.09,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還差點火候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:41.87,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}果然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:43.59,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}知道為什麼不可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:46.69,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因為戰隊題材的作品本身就很難通過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:48.80,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我知道不行但還是想試試看…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.18,0:16:50.77,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯  的確是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.35,0:16:51.85,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不過我覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.27,0:16:55.18,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這份企劃書把妳的喜好發揮得淋漓盡致
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:58.06,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這是非常重要的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:00.94,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這個遊戲的目標人群是哪些人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:03.94,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我計劃是以小孩子為目標的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:08.43,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}戰鬥部分就比較偏向成人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:11.93,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊  只要把目標群體集中到這二者之一…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:14.20,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯  就能做的更好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.50,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我改好後還能再給您拿來看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:17.37,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}當然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.69,0:17:21.13,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}對我來說  這個遊戲的戰鬥部分設計的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:23.04,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希望妳能以此為中心再拓展一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:24.15,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:30.41,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}企劃書可不是做得好就能通過的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:33.04,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是不會給妳添麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:35.21,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:37.92,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我有一對雙胞胎的弟弟妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:40.23,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}被他們倆誇獎說「遊戲真有趣啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:41.64,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:43.89,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:46.06,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還有  小青葉和初
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.32,0:17:49.90,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}她們都有自己的夢想和想做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:51.82,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我真的覺得她們很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:53.49,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以就在想…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:56.62,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只是隨波逐流地加入公司的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:58.87,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的可以繼續待在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:00.80,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妳不喜歡現在的工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:03.58,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒有那一回事  雖然我還不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:06.08,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可我真的很喜歡怪物和動物  工作真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:09.38,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}對於結音妳在工作上以及對工作的熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:11.17,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我們都是給予高度評價的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.74,0:18:14.42,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒有「跟周圍相比有優劣之分」的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:18.76,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}找到自己想做的事是不容易的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:22.22,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}至少我希望妳在找到之前能留在這間公司
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:25.78,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}結音也是團隊中不可或缺的一員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:27.14,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.76,0:18:30.61,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:32.27,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣所有人都問過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:34.78,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯  大家都好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.49,0:18:37.11,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}已經成為很棒的團隊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:38.82,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妳不這麼覺得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:40.28,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:44.24,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是那麼可愛的大家  還在等妳的新作品喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:47.41,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯  現在心情很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:48.12,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我會加把勁的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:52.08,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那麼  今晚要去賞櫻花嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:54.38,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}慰問品買什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:57.01,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妳還有工作所以要留在公司喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:18:58.36,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:18:59.44,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:06.06,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我做了點小菜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:08.52,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大家都嚐嚐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:10.48,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看起來真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:12.82,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我買了壽司過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:16.86,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}畢竟我沒辦法像遠山那樣自己做菜帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.95,0:19:18.90,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喔  真大方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:21.49,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我做了點甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:25.78,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我…拿了酒來…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:28.10,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}乾杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:30.76,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這個真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:34.48,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:37.20,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}果然凜做的料理最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:45.38,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:47.06,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:48.18,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:50.64,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不過這個看起來也好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.57,0:19:53.42,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}最肥美的這塊鮪魚我就收下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:19:57.69,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊  明明一個人分不到一個的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:19:59.74,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}先下手為強
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:02.08,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那我也要搶在被別人吃完之前下嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:05.16,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}青葉也吃一個  紀念工作一週年
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:07.14,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哎  真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:11.72,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊  芥末  這該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.15,0:20:14.50,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喔  妳怕吃芥末嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.66,0:20:16.02,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}才…才沒那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:17.25,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我能吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:20.34,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:28.28,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}小青葉  沒必要勉強自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:32.27,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}葉月小姐  剛才的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:34.38,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妳沒忘記吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.94,0:20:36.56,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要是妳修改內容的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.32,0:20:39.61,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}每改一次就…Bang！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:41.82,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}彈額頭  是彈額頭才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:45.03,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}企劃書的第二版！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.48,0:20:47.87,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我把戰鬥部分的點子增強過了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:50.08,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}咦  這就改好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:51.41,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不僅是己方角色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.46,0:20:52.66,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我把敵人也變成了五人眾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:55.96,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還試著把每個人都對應成了宿敵關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:20:58.88,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣就能獲得兩倍樂趣了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.22,0:21:00.12,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:02.52,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妳也不用這麼拼命…對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:08.04,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好了好了  看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:13.27,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}宴會也很盡興了  差不多該結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:16.98,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在最後  我有件重要的事情要宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.94,0:21:19.06,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}重要的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:20.65,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}到底是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:24.22,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}下一部作品的內容就快整合完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.60,0:21:28.60,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}於是呢  這次我也想舉行角色設計競賽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.15,0:21:33.68,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希望妳們能結合企劃書  發揮自己的想像力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:36.38,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}試著依照自己的喜好來設計角色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.82,0:21:39.72,new_game_main,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要是被採用了的話…
